= Conservative Parties [+ conservative_parties +]%

The Conservative parties of Germany honor fatherland, god and king. They are defined by their desire to uphold ancient traditions and creating a socially harmonious society. Whilst the specifics of what such a society and traditions might look vary a lot and differ, the Conservatives can largely agree that Marxism and Syndicalism are threats that should be dealt with, and are capable of presenting an united front as a result.

